---
title: Teriyaki Duck Rice Bowl with Garlic Pak Choi, Pickled Radish and Sesame Seeds
description: This Teriyaki Duck Rice Bowl is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R11_W19_UK_HVP18919-5_Main__5low-5796afaa.jpg
